# DP: Description: binutils bug workaround
# DP: Related bugs: #263601: m68k: workaround for binutils problem
# DP: Dpatch author: Roman Zippel <zippel@linux-m68k.org>
# DP: Patch author: Richard Zidlicky <rz@linux-m68k.org>
